[raw_stderr] +## API-Endpunkte
[raw_stderr] +
[raw_stderr] +### Produkte
[raw_stderr] +
[raw_stderr] +| Methode | Pfad | Beschreibung |
[raw_stderr] +| --- | --- | --- |
[raw_stderr] +| `GET` | `/api/products` | Gibt alle Sneaker zurueck |
[raw_stderr] +| `GET` | `/api/products/{id}` | Gibt einen Sneaker zurueck oder `404` |
[raw_stderr] +
[raw_stderr] +### Warenkorb
[raw_stderr] +
[raw_stderr] +| Methode | Pfad | Beschreibung |
[raw_stderr] +| --- | --- | --- |
[raw_stderr] +| `GET` | `/api/cart` | Gibt den aktuellen Warenkorb zurueck |
[raw_stderr] +| `POST` | `/api/cart/items` | Legt eine Warenkorbposition an |
[raw_stderr] +| `PATCH` | `/api/cart/items/{item_id}` | Aendert die Menge einer Position |
[raw_stderr] +| `DELETE` | `/api/cart/items/{item_id}` | Entfernt eine Position |
[raw_stderr] +
[raw_stderr] +Payload fuer `POST /api/cart/items`:
[raw_stderr] +
[raw_stderr] +```json
[raw_stderr] +{
[raw_stderr] +  "product_id": 1,
[raw_stderr] +  "size": "42",
[raw_stderr] +  "quantity": 1
[raw_stderr] +}
[raw_stderr] +```
[raw_stderr] +
[raw_stderr] +Payload fuer `PATCH /api/cart/items/{item_id}`:
[raw_stderr] +
[raw_stderr] +```json
[raw_stderr] +{
[raw_stderr] +  "quantity": 2
[raw_stderr] +}
[raw_stderr] +```
[raw_stderr] +
[raw_stderr] +### Bestellungen
[raw_stderr] +
[raw_stderr] +| Methode | Pfad | Beschreibung |
[raw_stderr] +| --- | --- | --- |
[raw_stderr] +| `POST` | `/api/orders` | Erstellt eine Bestellung aus dem aktuellen Warenkorb |
[raw_stderr] +| `GET` | `/api/orders/{id}` | Gibt eine Bestellung zurueck oder `404` |
[raw_stderr] +
[raw_stderr] +Payload fuer `POST /api/orders`:
[raw_stderr] +
[raw_stderr] +```json
[raw_stderr] +{
[raw_stderr] +  "shipping": {
[raw_stderr] +    "name": "Max Mustermann",
[raw_stderr] +    "street": "Musterstrasse 1",
[raw_stderr] +    "zip": "10115",
[raw_stderr] +    "city": "Berlin",
[raw_stderr] +    "country": "Deutschland",
[raw_stderr] +    "email": "max@example.com"
[raw_stderr] +  },
[raw_stderr] +  "payment_method": "credit_card"
[raw_stderr] +}
[raw_stderr] +```
[raw_stderr] +
[raw_stderr] +### Bewertungen
[raw_stderr] +
[raw_stderr] +| Methode | Pfad | Beschreibung |
