[raw_stderr] +
[raw_stderr] +```bash
[raw_stderr] +pytest
[raw_stderr] +```
[raw_stderr] +
[raw_stderr] +Falls `pytest` nicht installiert ist:
[raw_stderr] +
[raw_stderr] +```bash
[raw_stderr] +pip install pytest
[raw_stderr] +```
